					"name": "Hooks",
					"description": "* The party will learn about the lack of supply of ore and coal from Blackhill from the smiths in Broadhurst or Salthaven.\n* If the party completed the 'Road to Broadhurst' conventure and decide, after the fact, to investigate the source of the Raidenwight raid, they may track the raiding party back to Blackhill.  The leader of that raid is the Chief Ranger of Blackhill.\n* Following the road North to Blackhill will have the party discover the village.\n* There has been an increase in raiding activity on the roads between Salthaven and Broadhurst.  If this is investigated it will lead to the discovery of a Blackhill raiding party."
